## Install GeForce Experience

I installed version 3.27.0.112

### Bypass Geforce Experience Login:

Replace Geforce Experience app.js on this location:

`C:\Program Files\NVIDIA Corporation\NVIDIA GeForce Experience\www\`

with app.js from this github repository:

[GitHub - MOVZX/GFE-Login-Removal: Remove Mandatory Login of Geforce Experience - [support: v3.14.x <-> v3.20.x]](https://github.com/MOVZX/GFE-Login-Removal)

### Add games location to Geforce Experience Shield in settings part

Click on the gear icon (settings)

Go to shield section

Browse games and add them

